<div id="outline-container-sec-2" class="outline-2 activity">
<h2 id="sec-2"><span class="section-number-2">2</span> Combining NAND gates</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-2">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>NAND gates are said to be <i>universal logical gates</i> because you can make all other types of logic gate out of them.
</li>
<li>We can take a single NAND gate like this one.
</li>
</ul>
<object data="js/NANDabs.html" width='200px' height='100px'></object>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>And use it to make this
</li>
</ul>
<object data="js/ANDfromNANDS.html" width='300px' height='100px'></object>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>This is called an AND gate
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
