<h3 id="sec-6-1">Badge It - Platinum</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-6-1">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>There is a special arrangement of NAND gates called a D-Latch.
</li>
<li>Use the Web to find out what the arrangement of NAND gates in a D-Latch is.
</li>
<li>Write a description of a D-Latch and explain why it is useful in computing.
</li>
</ul>
